snippet.title: Red White & Bethune
snippet.description:
We are a family of 2 adults, 3 kids, and 6 dogs living in our remodeled 1983 Silver Eagle Bus! We are a Full-time Family that is always up for an adventure. We will take you along and show you America, through our lens!
Kyle- He's a huge lover of baseball and travel. He is more of the 'behind the scenes' kinda guy. He does all of our video editing and equipment handling. 
Jenn- She's a lover of all things makeup and fashion! Plus, she's super artsy fartsy and adores interior design.
Ben (9)- This kiddo has the kindest heart you'll every meet! You can find him exploring the outdoors or playing Fortnite in the evening with his buddies.
Molly (7)- She's a mini version of jean with double the sass! She LOVES to shop, get a mani pedi, and visit Starbucks. 
Eli (5)- He usually isn't wearing anything but underwear (and trust me, its a struggle to get him to keep those on). He can be spotted playing with his monster trucks in the dirt, or find a new stick.
